    "createdAt": "2026-06-02T14:07:28.309Z",
    "diffSummary": "Local persistence foundation (ADR-0005): a store/ layer on bundled SQLite (rusqlite) plus an encrypted credential store. A random 32-byte master key lives only in the OS keychain (keyring); the credential triple is AES-256-GCM sealed (random nonce, nonce||ciphertext) with that key and stored as ciphertext in SQLite — never plaintext. command/ persists the account+encrypted credential after QR/cookie/file login and restore_sessions re-logs-in saved accounts on startup (frontend auto-restore with a loading gate, QR only when none). Verified live on the real macOS keychain: the credential round-trips and the on-disk blob is ciphertext (no plaintext cookie value). config/logging.rs + redact.rs keep raw API captures redacted by default.",
    "changedFiles": [
        "src-tauri/Cargo.toml",
